Pillcam colon capsule (PCC) endoscopy is a novel strategy tool to inspect colon mucosa.

 The aim of the present study is to evaluate if PCC endoscopy is able to precisely investigate patients with ulcerative colitis and reach high consistency to conventional colonoscopy.

